Uses of Package
com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events

  • Packages that use com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events 
    Package Description
    com.opencredo.concursus.cassandra.events
    This package provides Cassandra implementations of the EventPersister, EventRetriever, AggregateCatalogue and EventStore interfaces, for persisting and retrieving event histories and keeping track of "live" aggregates.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events
    Defines the core Event type, and (in sub-packages) all of the things that can be done with events by event-handling middleware.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.batching
    Provides the EventBatch interface, which represents a collection of Events that are to be processed together, and two concrete implementations, ProcessingEventBatch (which sends batched events to an EventBatchProcessor on completion) and BufferingEventBatch (which stores up events for replaying to an interested observer on completion, before passing the batch on to some other EventsOutChannel).
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.cataloguing
    This package is concerned with maintaining an AggregateCatalogue to track "active" aggregates within the system.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.channels
    Event channels are how Events enter and leave the system.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.dispatching
    Provides the EventBus interface, which simplifies creating batches of events and dispatching them collectively into the system.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.filtering.batch  
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.filtering.channel  
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.filtering.log  
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.filtering.publisher  
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.history
    Provides the EventHistoryFetcher, which may be used to retrieve the event histories of one or more aggregates from an EventSource.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.indexing
    Provides the experimental EventIndex and EventIndexer interfaces, for classes which index aggregate ids by the most recent values assigned to parameters of events recorded against each aggregate.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.matching
    Provides the EventTypeMatcher interface, for classes that are able to match EventTypes to TupleSchemas.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.processing
    When an EventBatch completes, it is sent to an EventBatchProcessor (interface provided by this package).
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.publishing
    Provides the EventPublisher interface, representing an object that published Events to subscribers, and the EventSubscribable interface, which represents an object that event handlers can subscribe to.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.selection
    Provides the EventSelection utility class for selecting Events matching various criteria.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.sourcing
    Provides the EventSource and CachedEventSource interfaces, which represent sources of Events.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.state
    Defines the StateBuilder interface, which represents a class which can build an instance of a state class from an aggregate's event history, and the StateRepository interface, which represents a class that can retrieve state objects by aggregate id.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.storage
    Defines the EventStore interface, which represents an event store which can persist and retrieve events, and provides an InMemoryEventStore implementation.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.events.views
    Contains the JSON-serialisable EventView.
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.json.events  
    com.opencredo.concursus.domain.json.events.channels  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.dispatching  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.ordering  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.proxying  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.reflection  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.reflection.dispatching  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.reflection.interpreting  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.state  
    com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.pojos  
    com.opencredo.concursus.redis
